sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as Customer
  participant R as ROLLER
  participant P as PATCH
  participant API as Loyalty App API
  participant DB as App Database
  participant VIEW as Website or PWA
  participant EXT as External Events (CRUD)

  U->>R: Buy park pass
  opt External create source
    EXT->>R: Create booking event
  end
  R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Created)
  R->>P: Update loyalty field (purchase/edit)
  API->>DB: Save booking event
  alt Booking has child tickets linked to parent account
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (parent loyalty incremented by child stamps)
  else Standard booking
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (customer loyalty incremented)
  end
  API->>DB: Save PATCH loyalty snapshot

  U->>VIEW: Open loyalty view
  VIEW->>API: GET /account
  API->>DB: Read loyalty and reward state
  API-->>VIEW: Return updated loyalty status
  VIEW-->>U: Show loyalty progress

  opt Optional secondary sync mode (not fallback)
    API->>P: GET /v2/contacts?updatedSince={timestamp}
    API->>DB: Reconcile PATCH loyalty snapshot
  end

  alt Webhook processing fails
    API->>DB: Log failed webhook event only (no retry)
  end

  alt Loyalty target reached
    P->>R: Create one-time free-pass code
    alt PATCH automation webhook delivery
      P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/reward-code
      API->>DB: Save one-time free-pass code as available
    else PATCH custom-field delivery
      API->>P: GET /v2/contacts?email={customerEmail}
      API->>DB: Save one-time free-pass code from PATCH custom field
    end
    API->>DB: Apply counter reset rule (if enabled by park policy)
    VIEW-->>U: Show free pass code
  else Not yet at required amount
    VIEW-->>U: Show remaining points
  end

  alt External booking is edited
    EXT->>R: Update booking event
    R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Updated)
    R->>P: Update loyalty field (edit)
    API->>DB: Update booking state and loyalty state
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (loyalty recalculated)
    U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
    VIEW->>API: GET /account
    API-->>VIEW: Return updated booking and loyalty status
  end

  alt External booking is deleted
    EXT->>R: Delete booking event
    R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Cancelled)
    R->>P: Update loyalty field (delete)
    API->>DB: Update booking state and loyalty state
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated (loyalty recalculated)
    U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
    VIEW->>API: GET /account
    API-->>VIEW: Return updated booking and loyalty status
  end

  U->>R: Use free pass code at checkout
  R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/booking (Created or Updated)
  API->>DB: Mark reward booking as acquired

  U->>R: Redeem ticket at park entry
  R-->>API: POST /webhooks/roller/redemption (Created)
  API->>DB: Mark reward as used
  alt Reset policy
    R->>P: Update loyalty field (counter = 0)
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated
    API->>DB: Save reset PATCH loyalty snapshot
  else Rolling policy
    R->>P: Update loyalty field (counter reduced)
    P-->>API: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated
    API->>DB: Save rolled PATCH loyalty snapshot
  end
  U->>VIEW: Refresh loyalty view
  VIEW->>API: GET /account
  API-->>VIEW: Return reward used status
